Full Description: UNIMUNDO is an Internet TV; Video Sharing, Streaming Media, Social Community; with the best current videos; short movies, TV shows, funny; extreme videos; for creative and imaginative people who love to upload, share, and watch premium and official videos free. Uploading videos, sharing, participating or having a Channel in UNIMUNDO is free. Artists are able to upload their video productions under the respective Categories. Once a year, UNIMUNDO conducts the UNIMUNDO Awards to recognize videos and programs featured in UNIMUNDO as selected through the votes of the “Voting Members.” The UNIMUNDO Awards are designed to provide global exposure to Video Art and Video Content Creations and to position the imaginative and creative Artist or Producer among the best in the world. The member’s votes are tallied toward the selection of the winning Videos in each Category for the Annual Awards where the top videos in their respective Categories receive the Award. The “UNIMUNDO Choice Award” goes to the best Video of the year which is determined by having the highest vote by the Voting Members. A “Voting Member” is a “Registered Member.” There can only be one (1) winning video per Category and only one (1) video as the winner of the “UNIMUNDO Choice Award.” However, in the event of a tie in any of the Categories and/or of the Video for the Choice Award, those videos will be reset for new voting by the Voting Members. The final tally shall be concluded on the Thirtieth (30) day from the date the videos are republished for new votes at which time the voting will close and the winners will then be announced. Participation in UNIMUNDO is strictly voluntary and for the sole purpose of the Artists, Members and/or Producers gaining worldwide exposure for their videos.UNIMUNDO’s mission is to provide Entertainment Producers with a safe and positive environment to create exposure for their Videos, Programs, and Video Art Products and to help Producers share their Video creations by connecting with others all over the planet.

Description: Boulder Investment Group Reprise is an independent investment advisory practice.
Full Description: On the surface, Boulder Investment Group may look like a company that just manages investment assets for individuals, but it is really much more. The company focuses on its clients' needs and their comfort. Boulder creates a team of "care givers" who happen to work in the investment industry. From the moment clients walk through the doors at Boulder, they will feel the contentment and security that comes when they get a big warm hug from a friend. Clients' well-being is the company's primary concern so they can rest assured knowing that a competent and experienced advisor is in their corner looking after their financial health. Boulder uses a Core and Satellite approach. It is a system of managing money that allows Boulder to be very flexible with how it handles a client's investments. The core is made up of mutual funds and exchange-traded funds (ETFs). There are five different models that have increasing levels of risk and potential return. Boulder works with its clients to determine which of the five risk/return models to use, then it determines what percentage of their account should be in this "core" and what percentage should be allocated to the "satellite."

Continental Capital is a venture capital firm that analyzes and purchases charged-off assets from banks and financial institutions.
Full Description: Continental Capital is a venture capital firm that analyzes and purchases charged-off assets from banks and financial institutions. Its acquisition of these assets will result in the liquidation of a negative on books giving the bank a positive cash flow allowing recapitalization. Many banks and financial institutions in today's economic times are experiencing an increase in non-performing assets leading to more and more charge-offs.  Continental Capital Group consultants will evaluate and purchase any type of charge-off loans, from real estate to consumer lines of credit. Continental Capital Group's area of expertise is its ability to leverage the insight of its partners and current business associates from deal sourcing and due diligence through competitive analysis.
